764
00:33:49,443 --> 00:33:51,010
(SIGHS)

765
00:33:52,416 --> 00:33:53,816
Thank you.

766
00:33:53,983 --> 00:33:55,783
Good afternoon, Mr. Abdullah.

767
00:33:55,808 --> 00:33:58,450
I'm Officer Brent, I heard
