772
00:34:09,981 --> 00:34:12,129
I know that you're scared.

773
00:34:12,549 --> 00:34:14,934
But you have all these great
doctors taking care of you,

774
00:34:14,959 --> 00:34:17,598
- and I'll be here for you too.
